IAeBpelRegistry
public class AeBPWSBpelRegistry
extends AeAbstractBpelRegistry

Default impl of the IAeBpelRegistry.
Delegates all of the actual work retrieving readers to the AeDefReaderRegistry.
Delegates all of the actual work retrieving writers to the AeDefWriterRegistry.
